description:
After healing the daughter of Jairus by the sea of Galilee, Jesus now travels inland to his hometown, Nazareth. When you think of home, perhaps you think of a place of love and acceptance. He’s been looking to rest, and you’d think that he’d find it back home. But sadly, that’s not what happens at all.
